<p style="font-size:14px;color:#444;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;">
Great news! Your <strong>ATS-optimized resume</strong> tailored for <strong style="color:#7c3aed;">${esc(companyName)}</strong> has been successfully generated and is attached to this email as a <strong>PDF</strong>.
</p>
<div style="background:#f9f8ff;border-left:4px solid #7c3aed;padding:14px 18px;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;margin:0 0 24px;">
